        '5% of 300 → 0.05 \\times 300 = 15. OR \\frac{5}{100} \\times 300 = 15.',
        'Quick: 10% = ÷10. 1% = ÷100. 50% = ÷2. 25% = ÷4.',
        'For tricky ones, find 1% first, then scale.',
