        solution: 'C = \\pi \\times 14 \\approx 43.98 \\to 44.0 cm.' },
      { kind: 'fill-num', prompt: 'Circumference of a circle of radius 9 cm in cm to 1 d.p.', answer: 56.5, tol: 0.1,
        solution: '2 \\pi \\times 9 \\approx 56.55.' },
