        'a \\u2013 b: max = 3.65 \\u2013 13.5 = -9.85; min = 3.55 \\u2013 14.5 = -10.95.',
      ],
      example: 'Same a, b. Maximum of a + b is 18.15; minimum is 17.05.',
    },
    questions: [
